objective:
本課程主要教授學生以矩陣方法來處理結構問題，其包含六大方向: 1. 複習矩陣學 2. 結構矩陣學基本概念、3. 勁度法觀念、4. 勁度法解桁架問題、5. 勁度法解梁問題、6. 勁度法解剛架問題
The course contents are divided into 6 major topics: 1. Review the matrix theory; 2.Basic concepts of the matrix structural theory; 3. Stiffness method; 
4. Using stiffness method to solve truss problem; 5. Using stiffness method to solve beam problem; 6. Using stiffness method to solve rigid frame problem.
